de.hshannover.f4.trust.ifmapj.messages

Interface IdentifierHolder

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    MetadataHolder, PublishDelete, PublishNotify, PublishUpdate, ResultItem

    public interface IdentifierHolder
    Interface to access Identifier objects in elements that hold them. An element containing up to two Identifier objects, as it is the case for PublishUpdate, PublishNotify, PublishDelete ResultItem.
    Author:
    aw
